title: Percentage of U.S. population who are veterans in 2018 , by age and gender
summary: Overall Male is rapidly increasing, Female is gradually increasing,  throughout the Year
The order of lines according to average values of Percentage of population, in descending order is: 1. Male, and lastly, 2. Female.
The difference of Percentage of population between Male and Female is greater at Year 55_to_64_years compared to the Year 18_to_34_years.
